// @test regression/INV040-series-switch-const-arg
// @description A switch over series conditions yields a SERIES result; passing such a variable to a const-required param (plot title) is TV's CE10123. Condition-less switches stay unflagged. See INV040.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects errors: 1
// @expects error: line=8, message="Cannot call"

//@version=6
indicator("INV040")
trend = switch
    close > open => "Up"
    => "Flat"
mode = switch
    => "Static"
plot(close, title=trend)
plot(close, title=mode)
